lcls tour for slac employees lcls tour about the lcls tour make a reservation lcls facility map slac today lcls public site about the lcls tour on december 4 2008 slac staff will get the rare opportunity to take a sneak peek at the lcls slac badges are required for those joining the tour but no special training or certification is needed buses will depart parking lot c every 15 minutes from 9 00 am 11 00 am and from 2 00 pm 4 00 pm the tour will run the length of the lcls from the beam transport hall to the far experimental hall see the lcls facility map for more detail a few things to keep in mind before signing up for the tour the lcls walkthrough is approximately 3 4 of a mile in length there are no stairs but 45 minutes of steady walking is required with this in mind visitors are asked to wear comfortable flat closed toe shoes long pants are also required in addition please be advised that there are no working restroom facilities along the tour route reservations are required so sign up for the tour now reservations will close at noon on wednesday december 3 your browser does not have the ability to display inline frames you can view the content of this frame at this page slac footer your browser does not have the ability to display inline frames you can view the content of this frame at this page slac global navigation header privacy statement page contact
